er yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對記者資料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂][行動] 9月8點應對外國記者+3首歌歌詞+資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551469\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89f1887b5a386ba7f59aafe1272011343c7762f7","tid":1551531,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"包頭除帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9afded97c597c39626d6f681425aa7e9adb997","tid":1551531,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KH7q8Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KH7q8Q.jpg&h=86fc3ec1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"040ed08480807facd8b32b391f9b44104683fb0c","tid":1551531,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}